《'''亲爱的同志'''》（{{lang-ru|Дорогие товарищи!}}）是2020年俄罗斯[[时代剧|历史剧情片]]，由[[安德烈·康查洛夫斯基|安德烈·康查洛夫斯基]]执导、监制、编剧<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2020/film/global/andrei-konchalovsky-dear-comrades-films-boutique-1234721895/ |title=Andrei Konchalovsky's Venice Competition Title ''Dear Comrades'' Snapped Up by Films Boutique |work=Variety |access-date=2020-07-31 |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801191606/https://variety.com/2020/film/global/andrei-konchalovsky-dear-comrades-films-boutique-1234721895/ }}</ref>，获[[第77屆威尼斯影展|第77屆威尼斯影展]][[威尼斯影展評審團特別獎|评审团特别奖]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/07/venice-film-festival-2020-lineup-1234576400/|title=Venice Film Festival 2020 Full Lineup: Luca Guadagnino, Chloe Zhao, Gia Coppola, and More|last=Sharf|first=Zack|work=IndieWire|date=2020-07-28|access-date=2020-07-28|archive-date=2021-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319012244/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/07/venice-film-festival-2020-lineup-1234576400/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/2020/venezia-77-competition|title=Venezia 77 Competition|publisher=La Biennale di Venezia|website=labiennale.org|date=2020-07-28|access-date=2020-07-28|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728133557/https://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/2020/venezia-77-competition}}</ref>，代表俄罗斯参与[[第93届奥斯卡金像奖|第93届奥斯卡金像奖]][[奥斯卡最佳國際影片獎|最佳国际影片奖]]竞逐<ref name="Russia">{{cite web |url=http://www.tellerreport.com/life/2020-11-13-the-union-of-cinematographers-appreciated-the-nomination-for-the-%22oscar%22-of-the-film-%22dear-comrades!%22.SJI39f-2YD.html |title=The Union of Cinematographers appreciated the nomination for the "Oscar" of the film "Dear Comrades!" |work=Teller Report |date=2020-11-13 |access-date=2020-11-13 |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113140137/http://www.tellerreport.com/life/2020-11-13-the-union-of-cinematographers-appreciated-the-nomination-for-the-%22oscar%22-of-the-film-%22dear-comrades!%22.SJI39f-2YD.html }}</ref>，与另外14部电影入选短名单<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2021/film/news/oscars-shortlist-2021-makeup-visual-score-song-international-documentary-1234904174/ |title=Oscars Shortlists Announced in Nine Categories |work=Variety |first=Clayton |last=Davis |date=2021-02-09 |access-date=2021-02-10 |archive-date=2021-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311011416/https://variety.com/2021/film/news/oscars-shortlist-2021-makeup-visual-score-song-international-documentary-1234904174/ }}</ref>。影片讲述了1962年的[[新切尔卡斯克屠杀|新切尔卡斯克屠杀]]。

== 剧情 ==
1962年，[[新切尔卡斯克屠杀|新切尔卡斯克屠杀]]。地方市委党工柳德米拉是共产主义的坚定信仰者。新切尔卡斯克电力机车厂工人到市委大楼罢工期间，遭政府委员会下令开枪镇压，以此掩盖苏联爆发大型罢工行动的事实。行刑的时候，柳德米拉的女儿在刑场消失，彻底改变了柳德米拉对世界的看法。柳德米拉不顾当局大肆抓捕示威人士，在戒严的城市中四处寻找女儿的踪影。

